---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for Reave Automated — the rules and conditions for using our platform."
>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="doc">
      <div class="doc-header">
        <p class="doc-label">Legal</p>
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="doc-meta">Reave Automated &mdash; Last updated June 16, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-body">
        <section>
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using the Reave Automated platform ("Reave," "we," "us," or "our")
            at reave.app, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree,
            do not use the platform.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            Reave is an automated client communication platform that delivers requested information
            to clients via SMS, voice, and web interfaces. Features may change or be discontinued
            at any time without notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Eligibility</h2>
          <p>
            You must be at least 18 years old and legally capable of entering a binding agreement
            to use Reave. By using the platform you represent that you meet these requirements.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. SMS Communications</h2>
          <p>
            By providing your phone number and requesting information through the platform, you
            consent to receive transactional SMS messages from Reave Automated. These messages
            are sent solely in response to your explicit requests — no marketing or promotional
            messages will be sent.
          </p>
          <p>
            Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to opt out. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for
            assistance. Message and data rates may apply. Opt-out requests are processed immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Use the platform for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable law.</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the platform or its infrastructure.</li>
            <li>Submit false or misleading information.</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the platform's operation or servers.</li>
            <li>Use the platform to harass, spam, or harm others.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content, design, code, and materials on the platform are the property of Reave
            Automated or its licensors. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative
            works without express written permission.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The platform is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind,
            express or implied. We do not guarantee that the platform will be uninterrupted,
            error-free, or free of harmful components.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Reave Automated shall not be liable for any
            indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your
            use of or inability to use the platform.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>9. Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms at any time. Changes take effect when posted. Continued use
            of the platform after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by the laws of the Commonwealth of Massachusetts, without
            regard to its conflict of law provisions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>11. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these Terms? Reach us at
            <a href="mailto:support@reave.app">support@reave.app</a> or visit
            <a href="https://reave.app">reave.app</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  html,
  body {
    background: #050505;
  }

  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #050505;
    padding: 80px 24px 120px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .doc {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .doc-header {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    padding-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .doc-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .doc-meta {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .doc-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin: 0;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.15s, text-decoration-color 0.15s;
  }

  a:hover {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }
</style>
